{"total":38,"pageSize":12,"pageCount":4,"data":[{"title":"我和好朋友的聊天：童年的伤痛像一根掰不断的倒刺","uid":"c292240f5fd22263730c52f92d731b3f","slug":"talk-with-bf-about-family","date":"2022-06-24T16:00:00.000Z","updated":"2022-06-29T09:18:24.145Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/talk-with-bf-about-family.json","cover":"https://s2.loli.net/2022/06/29/MiP7DYCoEb1xmlc.png","text":"我总是自称「一个运气不怎么样的人」，每次抽奖基本都与奖品无缘，从小到大也没觉得经历过什么特别的好运爆棚的时刻，甚至玩游戏抽卡也平平无奇。 但只有一个方面，让我怀疑我是不是将运气都保留到这个地方了，那就是「结交好友」。 社会鱼龙混杂，谁都有遇人不淑的时候，因此我在此特指「好朋友」。...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"3k","symbolsTime":"3 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"我的人生哲学","slug":"我的人生哲学","count":7,"path":"api/categories/我的人生哲学.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"父母","slug":"父母","count":2,"path":"api/tags/父母.json"},{"name":"人生","slug":"人生","count":3,"path":"api/tags/人生.json"},{"name":"心理学","slug":"心理学","count":3,"path":"api/tags/心理学.json"}],"author":{"name":"桌沿","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"/img/me.png","link":"/","description":"桌沿奇思 Newsletter 主理人，少数派签约作者","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{"sspai":{"icon":"/svg/sspai.svg","link":"https://sspai.com/u/379wzx2e/posts"},"jike":{"icon":"/svg/jike.svg","link":"https://okjk.co/IktPrE"},"youtube":{"icon":"/svg/youtube.svg","link":"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCDHwHAiT-jJ4AACLHir70Fg"},"twitter":{"icon":"/svg/twitter.svg","link":"https://twitter.com/desksidezhuoyan"},"ins":{"icon":"/svg/instagram.svg","link":"https://www.instagram.com/deskside.zhuoyan/"},"mailto":{"icon":"/svg/mailto.svg","link":"mailto:deskside.zhuoyan@outlook.com"}}}},"feature":true},{"title":"一起来东湖边看日出","uid":"75c439f248c1d243c2186b93fab0e6e0","slug":"go-and-see-the-dawn","date":"2022-06-20T16:00:00.000Z","updated":"2022-06-29T09:26:28.288Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/go-and-see-the-dawn.json","cover":"https://s2.loli.net/2022/06/29/zCeRc3thoMLQw1a.png","text":"武汉大学北边的东湖浩浩汤汤，作为广州人的我第一次来到这里的时候，有被震撼到。 前几天，我被新认识的朋友妄为凌晨五点拉着来东湖边看日出，还是非常快乐的。我还在朋友圈写了一首小诗： 地平线的乌云高如城墙期待消沉了下去结果人山人海被一场小小雨冲走了大半接下来的栈桥就归愿意等待的人拥有了...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":231,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"生活录","slug":"生活录","count":2,"path":"api/categories/生活录.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"小确幸","slug":"小确幸","count":2,"path":"api/tags/小确幸.json"},{"name":"自然","slug":"自然","count":3,"path":"api/tags/自然.json"}],"author":{"name":"桌沿","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"/img/me.png","link":"/","description":"桌沿奇思 Newsletter 主理人，少数派签约作者","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{"sspai":{"icon":"/svg/sspai.svg","link":"https://sspai.com/u/379wzx2e/posts"},"jike":{"icon":"/svg/jike.svg","link":"https://okjk.co/IktPrE"},"youtube":{"icon":"/svg/youtube.svg","link":"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCDHwHAiT-jJ4AACLHir70Fg"},"twitter":{"icon":"/svg/twitter.svg","link":"https://twitter.com/desksidezhuoyan"},"ins":{"icon":"/svg/instagram.svg","link":"https://www.instagram.com/deskside.zhuoyan/"},"mailto":{"icon":"/svg/mailto.svg","link":"mailto:deskside.zhuoyan@outlook.com"}}}},"feature":true},{"title":"我们总爱追问意义","uid":"3bb428acc0dc8c539e0de5c0c4c23516","slug":"we-like-asking-about-meaning-of-life","date":"2022-06-17T16:00:00.000Z","updated":"2022-06-29T12:15:56.126Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/we-like-asking-about-meaning-of-life.json","cover":"https://s2.loli.net/2022/06/29/MiP7DYCoEb1xmlc.png","text":"我们总爱追问意义我们总是喜欢追问，XXX的意义是什么？ 学这个的意义是什么？活着的意义是什么？做这件事的意义是什么？过上更好的生活的意义是什么？…… 如果刨根问底，我们似乎总是会得到两个不同的结论，要么一切皆无意义，要么过程就是意义。 一切皆无意义不知道有多少读者朋友喜欢阅读科幻...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"1.6k","symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"我的人生哲学","slug":"我的人生哲学","count":7,"path":"api/categories/我的人生哲学.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"意义","slug":"意义","count":3,"path":"api/tags/意义.json"}],"author":{"name":"桌沿","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"/img/me.png","link":"/","description":"桌沿奇思 Newsletter 主理人，少